While the methods themselves are correctly wrapped as static, the shorthand properties for them are non-static. As an example, in AppBase.h:

        static bool GetDebuggerAttached();

Becomes (in CSModuleAtomicApp.cs):

      public bool DebuggerAttached
      {
         get
         {
            return GetDebuggerAttached();
         }
      }

      public static bool GetDebuggerAttached ()
      {
         return csb_AtomicApp_AppBase_GetDebuggerAttached_4925();
      }
